  "expert_review": {
    "design_styling": "The 2021 Porsche Macan embodies a sharper aesthetic appeal. Its front showcases a revamped nose, enriched with an inlay matching the exterior color. This design enhancement gives it a dominating presence on roads. The Macan GTS variant takes it up a notch with Its black-accented central nose section and other elements. Complementing its rear design is an eye-catching diffuser. The Macan lineup is further embellished with standard LED headlights equipped with the Porsche Dynamic Light System and Sport Design exterior mirrors.Porscheoffers a choice of larger wheels, starting at 19 inches for the Macan, 20 inches for the Macan S, and 21 inches for the GTS."
  },
  "verdict": "The Porsche Macan, while being the more compact and affordable SUV in Porsche's lineup, loses none of the exhilarating driving experience the brand is known for. Its popularity surpasses that of its larger sibling, the Cayenne, both globally and in India, attributable to its dynamic appeal. The Macan's allure lies in its ability to deliver robust performance packaged in a smaller, more agile form. This combination of power and compactness makes it highly attractive to a wide range of consumers. Its blend of size, power, and Porsche's signature driving experience makes it a standout choice for those seeking the thrill of a sports car in a more practical SUV form.",
